item.title: AG Nations Cup 2015 grand final stream
item.dc:creator: fury
item.description:
Hey guys. Since AG Nations Cup 2015 Grand Finals are played in Double Elimination and Team Belarus (Loser Bracket winners) won Round 1 of the Grand Final, I will stream Round 2 today.
If you are interessted in watching, check twitch.tv/bo0giem4n
The match will be played in BO7 (Winner will be the best of 7 maps, each map 20 minutes playtime).

Edit: The game has been resheduled. Sorry guys. I will inform you here when they will play their match.
